   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3166_0010-1"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="org" ref="#pmb29442">Frankfurter Zeitung</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">(<rs type="org" ref="#pmb29442"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Gazette de Francfort</foreign></rs>).</hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Fondateur M.</foreign><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb87771">L. Sonnemann</rs>.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb36344" subtype="implied">Journal</rs> politique,
                        financier,</hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print">commercial et littéraire.</hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Paraissant trois fois par jour.</hi></hi></foreign></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Bureau à <rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs>:</hi></hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs></hi>, <date when="1896-01-13">13. Januar</date>.</seg></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb42671">24. Rue Feydeau</rs>.</hi></hi></foreign></seg><salute rend="center">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Ich le<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e eben das <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02763-1"/><rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb92950">Referat</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02763-1"><bibl><rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb4986">m.</rs> [ = <rs type="person" ref="#pmb4986">Fedor Mamroth</rs>]: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb92950">Schauspielhaus</rs>. In: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb36344">Frankfurter
                        Zeitung</rs>, Jg. 40, Nr. 12, <date when="1896-01-12">12. 1. 1896</date>,
                     Zweites Morgenblatt, S. 1</bibl>. <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb92950">Rezension</rs> der Premiere von <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29917">Liebelei</rs> am <rs type="org" ref="#pmb34987">Frankfurter Städtischen
                     Schauspielhaus</rs>; <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1896-01-11" subtype="see"/>. </note> meines <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb4986">Onkels</rs> und finde es wunder<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön. Zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen Dir und ihm<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind
               jetzt hoffentlich alle <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02763-2"/>Mißver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tändni<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02763-2">wohl aufgrund
                  wiederholter Ablehnungen <rs type="person" ref="#pmb4986">Mamroths</rs>, <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb30257 #pmb31965 #pmb30117 #pmb30453">Werke</rs> von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs>
                  abzudrucken</note> be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eitigt. Eine be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ere Einführung in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb151">Deut<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chland</rs> konnte man für Dein <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb29917">Stück</rs> kaum erträumen. Ich beglückwün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che
               Dich innig zu Deinem neuen Erfolge und danke Dir für Deine lieben Grüße aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb146">Frankfurt</rs>.</p><closer>In Treue <lb/>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmnn</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
